sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant RBACProxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8432/TCP HTTPS Bearer
    participant Gorch as Guardrails Orchestrator<br/>8032/TCP HTTPS
    participant Detector as Detector InferenceService<br/>443/TCP HTTPS/gRPC mTLS
    participant Generator as Generator InferenceService<br/>443/TCP HTTPS/gRPC mTLS
    participant OTLP as OTLP Collector<br/>gRPC TLS1.2+

    Note over Client,OTLP: Flow 2: Guardrails Request Orchestration

    Client->>Router: POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Router->>RBACProxy: Forward (reencrypt TLS)
    RBACProxy->>RBACProxy: Validate OAuth Token<br/>SubjectAccessReview
    RBACProxy->>Gorch: Forward Request<br/>8032/TCP HTTPS
    Gorch->>Detector: Check Guardrails<br/>mTLS Service Identity
    Detector-->>Gorch: Detection Results
    Gorch->>Generator: Inference Request<br/>mTLS Service Identity
    Generator-->>Gorch: Prediction Response
    Gorch->>OTLP: Export Telemetry<br/>gRPC TLS1.2+
    Gorch-->>RBACProxy: Response
    RBACProxy-->>Router: Response
    Router-->>Client: JSON Response
